nefit+Plans&amp;rft.pub=Settlement+Benefits+Association&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.settlementbenefits.com%2Fpolicy-owners%2Ffaqs%2Fquestions-about-long-term-care-benefit-plans&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALong+Term+Care+Benefit+Plan\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-cefa-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-cefa_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-cefa_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-cefa_4-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cefa.fsu.edu/content/download/110537/1027460/file/Medicaid%20Final%20Report%201-19-12.pdf\">\"Conversion of Life-Insurance Policies to Long-Term Care Benefit Plans in Florida\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. Florida State University. January 2012<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 22,</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Conversion+of+Life-Insurance+Policies+to+Long-Term+Care+Benefit+Plans+in+Florida&amp;rft.pub=Florida+State+University&amp;rft.date=2012-01&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cefa.fsu.edu%2Fcontent%2Fdownload%2F110537%2F1027460%2Ffile%2FMedicaid%2520Final%2520Report%25201-19-12.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALong+Term+Care+Benefit+Plan\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-cpr-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-cpr_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-cpr_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cpreports.com/2014/06/17/how-men-can-guard-agianst-po